Package neqsim.processSimulation.processEquipment.compressor

Class CompressorChartAlternativeMapLookup

java.lang.Object
neqsim.processSimulation.processEquipment.compressor.CompressorChartAlternativeMapLookup
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, CompressorChartInterface
public class CompressorChartAlternativeMapLookup extends Object implements CompressorChartInterface, Serializable
This class is an implementation of the compressor chart class that uses Fan laws and "double" interpolation to navigate the compressor map (as opposed to the standard class using reduced variables according to Fan laws).
Version:
$Id: $Id
Author:
asmund
